From 59c658cc714ad2ec6093a23754c54d5742dfe648 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Derek J. Clark" <derekjohn.clark@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2026 20:23:50 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] fix(Hardware Support): Add missing and clean up AYANEO
 devices - Adds KONKR Fit and Suiplay x01 to configurations - While at it,
 adds capability filter to AYANEO configurations to reduce   the reported
 capabilities lists to the supported events.

